131
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:41,790
It's just different.

132
00:06:41,790 --> 00:06:44,250
We have a different path
that we're going to follow.

133
00:06:44,250 --> 00:06:49,830
And so as things change, market
dynamics will change with them.

