623
00:28:25,540 --> 00:28:29,560
house, whether it's avoiding a
certain situation because you

624
00:28:29,560 --> 00:28:32,740
know that it would likely
turn into a very bad accident,

625
00:28:32,740 --> 00:28:37,440
like driving after you've
had too much to drink--

626
00:28:37,440 --> 00:28:42,120
if you've ever done anything
that involves pulling back

627
00:28:42,120 --> 00:28:45,660
from taking a risk,
it's because you have

628
00:28:45,660 --> 00:28:48,400
felt pain, either current pain.

629
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:55,140
Or you have felt the
memory of previous pain.

630
00:28:55,140 --> 00:28:57,450
Now let me ask you a question.

631
00:28:57,450 --> 00:29:02,860
Suppose none of you
are feeling any pain.

632
00:29:02,860 --> 00:29:05,300
Will you actually be
able to control yourself

633
00:29:05,300 --> 00:29:08,330
from taking on certain risks?

634
00:29:08,330 --> 00:29:12,970
So this gets back to the
