635
00:29:12,970 --> 00:29:16,720
If in 2004 or 2005,
you were at one

636
00:29:16,720 --> 00:29:18,760
of these financial
institutions that

637
00:29:18,760 --> 00:29:21,210
invested in these
kinds of securities

