651
00:30:13,610 --> 00:30:17,720
circuitry that cocaine does.

652
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:18,620
I'm not kidding.

653
00:30:18,620 --> 00:30:20,760
This is not an
analogy or a metaphor.

654
00:30:20,760 --> 00:30:22,430
It's a physiological fact.

655
00:30:22,430 --> 00:30:25,190
Neuroscientists
using fMRI machines

656
00:30:25,190 --> 00:30:29,330
had individuals play games
