1061
00:49:12,960 --> 00:49:14,430
in industry.

1062
00:49:14,430 --> 00:49:18,840
And it's an extraordinarily
flexible and powerful method,

1063
00:49:18,840 --> 00:49:24,060
again, based on the principle
