1064
00:49:24,060 --> 00:49:28,590
We then started introducing risk
into the picture explicitly.

1065
00:49:28,590 --> 00:49:31,980
We talked about the size effect,
January effect, value line,

1066
00:49:31,980 --> 00:49:36,780
